item.title: About
item.description: Don’t hire us. We’re not the cheapest and we’re not the best. We don’t have decades of experience and none of us have MFAs. We’re simply a small group of designers, in love with practicality. We don’t produce “good” design, we produce ampl design. You’re looking for trendy? Hire someone else. You want timeless? We’re ready when you are.
